ll not be overburdened and time will be properly managed to complete the\r\ncourse content.</span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>2)<span xss=removed>    \r\n</span></span></span><span xss=removed>There\r\nshould be a proper guideline about MCQ so that it can improve the knowledge,\r\nskills and attitude of students.</span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>3)<span xss=removed>    \r\n</span></span></span><span xss=removed>There\r\nshould be a proper guideline about OSPE considering different domains of\r\nobjectives and OSPE should be conducted centrally.</span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>4)<span xss=removed>    \r\n</span></span></span><span xss=removed>There\r\nshould be standard and uniformed checklist for procedure station and that\r\nshould be practiced in all medical colleges.</span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>5)<span xss=removed>    \r\n</span></span></span><span xss=removed>There\r\nshould be clear instructions about self learning that is assignment and self\r\nassessment.</span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>6)<span xss=removed>    \r\n</span></span></span><span xss=removed>Formative\r\nassessment procedure should be maintained by all medical colleges.</span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>7)<span xss=removed>    \r\n</span></span></span><span xss=removed><span xss=removed> </span>Small group teaching and Problem based\r\nlearning should be practiced by adequate number of skilled teaching staffs.</span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>8)<span xss=removed>    \r\n</span></span></span><span xss=removed>There\r\nis integrated teaching in our curriculum but it should be practiced by all\r\nmedical colleges.</span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>9)<span xss=removed>    \r\n</span></span></span><span xss=removed><span xss=removed> </span>Adequate number of skilled teaching and\r\ntechnical staffs should be ensured in all medical colleges by the specific body\r\nof Government.</span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>10)<span xss=removed>                       \r\n</span></span></span><span xss=removed>Promotion\r\nof an appropriate educational environment which is the soul and spirit of\r\nmedical curriculum. Collaborative rather than competitive environment helps\r\nstudents to learn and to develop a spirit of team work.</span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>11)<span xss=removed>                       \r\n</span></span></span><span xss=removed>Resources\r\nneeded to deliver the curriculum which may be lecture hall, laboratory space\r\nand laboratory equipments, sufficient number of tutorial rooms should be\r\nensured in all medical colleges by the specific body of Government.</span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p xss=removed><span xss=removed> </span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p xss=removed><b xss=removed><span xss=removed>Implementation :</span></b></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>1)<span xss=removed>    \r\n</span></span></span><span xss=removed>Experts\r\nof Biochemistry and Physiology will focus on the overlapping contents of above\r\nmentioned cards and make it well defined and student centered.</span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>2)<span xss=removed>    \r\n</span></span></span><span xss=removed>MCQs\r\nand OSPEs can be collected from different medical colleges and a question bank\r\ncan be made. Wokshops on preparation of MCQ and preparation and conduction of OSPE\r\ncan be conducted in different medical colleges under the supervision of experts\r\nof CME.</span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>3)<span xss=removed>    \r\n</span></span></span><span xss=removed>To\r\naugment the core curriculum some elective program related to core like project\r\nwork can be added, which will facilitate higher level of objectives.</span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>4)<span xss=removed>    \r\n</span></span></span><span xss=removed><span xss=removed> </span>Elective programme like computer literacy\r\nprogramme can be added which will help student in E-learning.</span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p xss=removed><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>5)<span xss=removed>    \r\n</span></span></span><span xss=removed><span xss=removed> </span>All medical colleges should maintain Medical\r\neducation units to develop skilled teaching staffs for proper implementation of\r\ncurriculum to achieve the National goal and It should be monitored by\r\nGovernment regularly.</span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p xss=removed><span xss=removed>Curriculum is a continuous, never ending process. So the\r\nneeds of the individual students, educational institutions and the community\r\nmust be assessed and this dynamic process works best in an environment\r\nconductive to learning, thrives on monitoring, quality assurance and continuous\r\nquality improvement. </span></p><p>\r\n\r\n</p><p xss=removed><span xss=removed> </span></p><p>\r\n\r\n<b></b><i></i><u></u><sub></sub><sup></sup><strike></strike><br></p>', '2018-01-19 17:01:19', 'upload/attachment/fd43b26d18d49cbf232979eb7101b8ed.doc', '<p><span xss=removed>Thanks for your job. The strength, weakness and improvements part of your assignments are excellent, but implementation part is not satisfy the expected points .  By regular faculty training, discussion & dialogue with the authority, and curriculum mapping are the way to implement.</span></p><p><span xss=removed>Prof Md Shah Alam(MBBS,DTCD, MCPS,MMEd)</span></p><p><span xss=removed>Prof &Head, Forensic Medicine, Ibrahim Medical college.<br></span><br></p>', NULL, '2018-01-19 23:01:19', NULL),
