nt\r\nthat transform teacher centre to learner centre learning. Digital library in\r\nmedical college can be introduced<span xss=removed>  </span>like\r\ndifferent engineering Colleges.<o></o></span></span></font></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" xss=removed>\r\n\r\n</p><p class="MsoNormal" xss=removed><span class="fontstyle01"><span xss=removed><o><font color="#242021"> </font></o></span></span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" xss=removed>\r\n\r\n</p><p class="MsoNormal" xss=removed>&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;<font color="#242021"><span class="fontstyle01"><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>·<span xss=removed><font size="3">        \r\n</font></span></span></span></span>&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;<span class="fontstyle01"><span xss=removed>More emphasis should be given on professionalism.<o></o></span></span></font></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" xss=removed>\r\n\r\n</p><p class="MsoNormal" xss=removed><span class="fontstyle01"><span xss=removed><o><font color="#242021"> </font></o></span></span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" xss=removed>\r\n\r\n</p><p class="MsoNormal" xss=removed><span class="fontstyle01"><span xss=removed><o><font color="#242021"> </font></o></span></span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" xss=removed>\r\n\r\n</p><p class="MsoNormal" xss=removed><span class="fontstyle01"><span xss=removed><o><font color="#242021"> </font></o></span></span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" xss=removed>\r\n\r\n</p><p class="MsoNormal" xss=removed><font face="Calibri"><b><span xss=removed><span xss=removed> </span>How to implement</span></b><span xss=removed>:<o></o></span></font></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" xss=removed>\r\n\r\n</p><p class="MsoNormal" xss=removed>&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;<font color="#242021"><span class="fontstyle01"><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>·<span xss=removed><font size="3">        \r\n</font></span></span></span></span>&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;<span class="fontstyle01"><span xss=removed>Case based curricula may be helpful for integration by focusing\r\nlearning around a series of clinical cases.<o></o></span></span></font></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" xss=removed>\r\n\r\n</p><p class="MsoNormal" xss=removed>&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;<span xss=removed><span xss=removed>·<span xss=removed>        \r\n</span></span></span>&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;<font color="#242021"><span class="fontstyle01"><span xss=removed>It is recognized\r\nthat all doctors should have some competence as teachers and skills in\r\nteaching. <u>So training of teachers</u> is important. The wider community of\r\npotential teachers is essential for implementing curriculum.</span></span><span xss=removed><o></o></span></font></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" xss=removed>\r\n\r\n</p><p class="MsoNormal" xss=removed><span xss=removed><o><font face="Calibri"> </font></o></span></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" xss=removed>\r\n\r\n</p><p class="MsoNormal" xss=removed>&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;<font color="#242021"><span class="fontstyle01"><span xss=removed><span xss=removed>·<span xss=removed><font size="3">        \r\n</font></span></span></span></span>&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;<span class="fontstyle01"><span xss=removed><span xss=removed> </span>Recognisation on e-learning\r\nshould be given,<span xss=removed>  </span></span></span><span class="fontstyle21"><span xss=removed><span xss=removed> </span></span></span><span class="fontstyle01"><span xss=removed>it is not only about knowledge transfer, </span></span><span class="fontstyle21"><span xss=removed>on</span></span><span class="fontstyle01"><span xss=removed>-line learning can be effective and efficient for future doctor. E- Learning\r\nprovides an environment that transform teacher centre to learner centre\r\nlearning. Digital library in medical college can be introduced like different\r\nengineering Colleges.<o></o></span></span></font></p><p align="center" class="MsoNormal" xss=removed>\r\n\r\n</p><p 