(40, 29, 'Educational Objectives and Competencies ', 'Assignment: Taxonomy and Learning Objectives in Educational Program.  \r\n\r\nFormulation of specific objectives according to the hierarchies in different learning domain.\r\n', '2018-02-01 06:59:14', 'upload/attachment/885b76f05d38a8d2efb3eb2b9e44539c.docx', '<p class="MsoListParagraph" xss=removed>&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;A.<span xss=removed>     \r\n</span>&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;Understanding the definition: Satisfactory\r\n(which you have described in the introduction)<o></o></p><p class="MsoNormal">Importance of Toxonomy & objectives:<o></o></p><p class="MsoNormal">Your write up is Ok. But the fact that understanding of\r\ntheir importance is very much necessary for its future practical use by yourself.\r\nIt would be better if you have written their importance in your own language or\r\nwith example.<o></o></p><p class="MsoNormal">Your write up of objectives:<o></o></p><p class="MsoNormal">Most of them are good. You have used action verbs, contents\r\nare mostly appropriate and you have also used criteria in some of them.<o></o></p><p class="MsoNormal"> In objective no 9,,\r\n10, 12 you have used the verb ‘ understand’ which is nor measurable. It may be\r\nwritten as will be able to ‘express the understanding’ or ‘describe’ the …….<o></o></p><p class="MsoNormal">In Objective no 13: ‘will be able to calculate of atherosclerotic\r\nrisk of an individual using lipoprotein and apoproteins as laboratory tools’\r\nmay be better option as they need to learn the calculation.<o></o></p><p class="MsoNormal"> In obj. 16 the verb\r\n‘formulate” may be better expressed than ‘make out’ In obj. 17 the verb\r\n‘describe’ mey be used. <o></o></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class="MsoNormal"> In obj. 27 the\r\nsentence may start with the verb ‘create’ awareness <o></o></p>', 'upload/attachment/0910922f5bfb61fa081bb30c2f450733.docx', '2018-02-01 12:59:14', 'F'),
