(50, 39, 'Impotance of Taxonomy and learning objectives in educational program and some specific objectives on a selective topic', 'Impotance of Taxonomy and learning objectives in educational program and some specific objectives on a Food, Nutrition & Nutritional factors on diseases', '2018-01-26 05:47:29', 'upload/attachment/c88e8f58c7f74dc005e153007e097242.pdf', '<p>Thanks for submitting your assignment. You have nicely mentioned different taxonomy of the topic.</p><p>However, please Correct some objectives as</p><p>1. In cognitive domain avoid the action verve like describe-- as you can not measure it ( Mention six points on--------)</p><p>In cognitive domain, justify is not suitable.</p><p>2. In psychomotor domain---- Draw and level is ok, But to measure BMI--- better put 3-4 scenerio of patient and then allow to calculate</p><p>3. In affective domain, you can show some photograph  patient of malnutrition, marasmus, morbid obese--- then ask to counsel the patient.</p><p>4. Raise the social problems of fast food---.</p><p><br></p><p> thanks again.</p>', NULL, '2018-01-26 11:47:29', 'F'),
