(60, 50, 'Assignment: Taxonomy and Learning Objectives in Educational             Program. Specific objectives according to the hierarchies in different learning domain.', '', '2018-01-28 02:59:14', 'upload/attachment/d5fb55ca82a55a2a9bcaefa86c7c7940.docx', '<p>Thanks for your much effort for preparing  assignment. Your assignment fulfills majority of the concept which we want to judge. But I have some observation. </p><p>Taxonomy usually help to classify learning objectives;setting learning experience and learning objectives are the basis for designing curriculum,content,evaluation. </p><p>Every specific objectives should have at least two things- <b>Task</b>(which include <u>act/action verb</u>, <u>Content</u> & <u>Condition</u>)  and <b>criteria</b>. The verb ''Perform'' should use for psycho-motor domain. In cognitive domain whether the learner satisfy/encourage/take safety measure.</p><p> Please rewrite accordingly and submit today. Every fellow should also mention her name/ID no.</p><p>Prof Md Shah Alam</p>', NULL, '2018-01-28 08:59:14', 'F');
