t;!--[endif]--&gt;<span xss=removed>Select the key content area- Whether Teaching-learning or\r\nResearch or Administration. Then select the sub-skill of each component.\r\nSuppose aim is to improve teacher’s skill in clinical teaching or lecturing, or\r\nsmall group discussion, or feedback, or evaluation.<o></o></span></p><p xss=removed>&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;<span xss=removed>b.<span xss=removed>      \r\n</span></span>&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;<span xss=removed>S<b>elect the strategies for\r\npersonal development, educational leadership, organizational development and\r\nchanges.</b> Also strategies in teaching specific content area like\r\ninter-professionalism, communication skill, or curriculum design.<o></o></span></p><p xss=removed>&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;<span xss=removed>c.<span xss=removed>       \r\n</span></span>&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;<span xss=removed>Determine the target  population:  All health care professional involve in\r\nteaching, organizational staff support teaching and organization etc.<o></o></span></p><p xss=removed>&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;<span xss=removed>3.<span xss=removed>      \r\n</span></span>&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;<b><span xss=removed>Select\r\nthe educational format,Implement & evaluate</span></b><span xss=removed>:\r\n<o></o></span></p><p xss=removed>&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;<span xss=removed>a.<span xss=removed>      \r\n</span></span>&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;<span xss=removed>Workshop, seminars, fellowship etc.<o></o></span></p><p xss=removed>&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;<span xss=removed>b.<span xss=removed>      \r\n</span></span>&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;<span xss=removed>Integrated longitudinal program can be adopted alternative to\r\nfellowship program where the faculty commit to use 10-20% of their time for\r\nnext 1-2yrs for maintaing teaching, research & administrative\r\nresponsibilities in addition to own development.<o></o></span></p><p xss=removed>&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;<span xss=removed>c.<span xss=removed>       \r\n</span></span>&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;<span xss=removed>Decentralized activates<o></o></span></p><p xss=removed>&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;<span xss=removed>d.<span xss=removed>      \r\n</span></span>&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;<span xss=removed>Peer-coaching<o></o></span></p><p xss=removed>&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;<span xss=removed>e.<span xss=removed>      \r\n</span></span>&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;<span xss=removed>Micro-teaching<o></o></span></p><p xss=removed>&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;<span xss=removed>f.<span xss=removed>        \r\n</span></span>&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;<span xss=removed>E-learning<o></o></span></p><p xss=removed>&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;<span xss=removed>4.<span xss=removed>      \r\n</span></span>&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;<b><span xss=removed>Mentorship</span></b><span xss=removed>:\r\ncommon strategies to promote socialization & development. Also balance  in three key element-support, challenge and\r\nvision for future<o></o></span></p><p xss=removed>&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;<span xss=removed>5.<span xss=removed>      \r\n</span></span>&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;<span xss=removed>Self directed learning program<o></o></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p xss=removed><span xss=removed><o> </o></span></p><p><br></p><p>your sumission by email-</p><p class="MsoNormal"><b>DEVELOPMENT   OF  EDUCATIONAL \r\nENVIRONMENT & STAFF<o></o></b></p><p class="MsoNormal"><b>General\r\nconsideration:</b><o></o></p><p class="MsoNormal">Environment of any educational setting has got direct effect\r\nupon the learners. It is more important in medical science. The primary aim of\r\nmedical education is to make a safe doctor. \r\nSomeone might  give emphasis on\r\nthe humanitarian quality , but if we think about the ward safety deeply, we can\r\n  understand \r\nit encompass   everything  in achieving potentials to become a good\r\ndoctor. Teachers or facilitators   who are involved  in this process is an important factor to\r\ntransfer batons of morality & clinical acumen to future generation. But we\r\nare to remember   that only human being\r\ncannot help the  learners   to\r\nreach the all objectives of   education.\r\nAvailability of adequate logistics & infrastructure   of the teaching environment are  also \r\nequally important.<o></o></p><p class="MsoNormal"> In ancient time as\r\ndescribed in MOHAVAROT the learners usually stayed in house of the teacher as a\r\nfamily member & GURU or the teacher taught the intended subject for which\r\nthe student or SISHYA came. This scenario is not compatible with modern era. Life\r\nhas become complicated in many aspects. Today’s \r\nmentorship & belonging \r\ntheme  of learning module\r\nrepresent some aspects of this old system.  Assessment was mostly  formative \r\n& unidirectional  at that time\r\nas only the GURU had power to give exit  \r\naward to the SISHYA or learner. Later on during BUDDHA era large group\r\nlearning system came out rather one teacher one student  concept of GURUGRIHA sikkha or whole time\r\nresidential teachingunder single teacher.  \r\nNalanda , mohasthan garh or moynamoti \r\nBUDDHA BIHAR  could be cited as an\r\nexample of old campus oriented learning saytem, which are being still\r\nrepresented by  the modern universities\r\nor residential schools & colleges <o></o></p><p class="MsoNormal">In present time after invention of computer&  internet \r\nbased  virtual learning system the\r\ncampus based learning model  is    replaced the on campus courses to distance\r\ncourse or blended together to reach the target of structured  or pinpoint aim of modern education.<o></o></p><p class="MsoNormal"><o> </o></p><p class="MsoNormal"><b>COMPONANTS   OF EDUCATIONAL ENVIRONMENT:<o></o></b></p><p class="MsoNormal">If we want to bring some change in present structure of\r\neducation ,  with an aim to improve it we\r\nare to split the system into small components so that it become easy to\r\nunderstand to which point, what type of change is demanded & changing\r\nemphasis is to be given.<o></o></p><p class="MsoNormal">Aimed or targeted  \r\neducational environment has the following components: <o></o></p><p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst" xss=removed>&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;a)<span xss=removed>     \r\n</span>&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;Learners classification ( undergrads/ post\r\ngrads/ adult/ children)<o></o></p><p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" xss=removed>&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;b)<span xss=removed>     \r\n</span>&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;Course or curriculum<o></o></p><p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" xss=removed>&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;c)<span xss=removed>      \r\n</span>&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;Teachers or supervisors, administrators.<o></o></p><p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" xss=removed>&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;d)<span xss=removed>     \r\n</span>&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;Physical environments<o></o></p><p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpLast" xss=removed>&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;e)<span xss=removed>     \r\n</span>&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;Logistic support( budget , inanimate objects\r\n& technical manpower)<o></o></p><p class="MsoNormal"><b>LEARNERS\r\nCLASSIFICATION: </b> like any other\r\ndevelopmental programme in medical education \r\nto whom the facilitators are intentended for  should be the cleared .  Modules for undergrads and post grades differ\r\nin several aspect. Faculty members should know which domain of learning should\r\nget priority in developing themselves to attain the goal of objectives. Staffs\r\nspecially those who are giving technical support to the learners are to improve\r\nthemselves according to the need of course and curriculum. If these peoples are\r\nprofessional  then time could be saved in\r\nthe course. Again grading the learners also important in staff development\r\nprogramme, as for example teachers when facilitates a 3<sup>rd</sup> year\r\nclinical clerking will not be same with 5<sup>th</sup> year students. Learning\r\ntheory  in lectures differs in many ways\r\nin ward set teaching.<o></o></p><p class="MsoNormal"><b><span xss=removed>COURSE\r\n& CURRICULUM</span> : </b> In making\r\ncourse or curriculum for the staff development programme we are to keep in mind\r\nthat teachers  are  adult learners. They are doing the things\r\nalready in their settings,  so actually\r\nmuch of adult learning is relearning, in a structured way. Other factors that\r\nare to be considered in adult staff development programme  are motivation, expectation, experience  of learners may not go with a prefixed seat\r\nprogramme. It has to be tailored according to local culture and situation. For\r\nassessing developmental  learning,   feedback is more effective then test so this\r\nis to be practiced in course. \r\nInteractive lecture, small group discussion, self directed learning,\r\nmicroteaching, E learning, feed back from learners and many other modality\r\ncould be included in curriculum \r\naccording to needs & priorities.<o></o></p><p class="MsoNormal"><b> FACILITATORS, ADMINISTRATORS, & TECHNICAL\r\nSTAFFS.<o></o></b></p><p class="MsoNormal">Though all are involved in providing good educational\r\nenvironment , we are more concerned about the facilitators/ teachers. In a\r\nsurgical  faculty developmental programme\r\nfollowing methods can be adopted.<o></o></p><p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpFirst" xss=removed>&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;a)<span xss=removed>     \r\n</span>&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;Mentoring: \r\nmentor is one who is guide , friend, philosopher,  trainer ,advisor, career planner. It is a\r\ncomplex multidimensional activities generally observed in senior experienced\r\nfaculty.  In  the discipline of surgery mentoring could be\r\na good model in learning process. As surgery needs craftsmanship, demands  humanitarian approach in management of\r\nterminally ill surgical patients, to have patience in facing surgical\r\ncomplications ,major trauma, breaking bad news of malignancy, to develop\r\nmanagarial  capacity in the ward, to\r\nhave  an exceptional  skill in communication regarding  informed consent; mentor ship development may\r\nhelp in meeting demand of all  these.\r\nSpecially in learning the technicalities of safe skill a mentor can help a less\r\nexperienced junior in learning .<o></o></p><p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle">Disadvantage of this system is that a\r\nmentor can’t  be instantly made &   there\r\nis no structured curriculum to become a mentor. It is an inborn , innate\r\ncapability which is an ongoing career long journey.<o></o></p><p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><o> </o></p><p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" xss=removed>&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;b)<span xss=removed>     \r\n</span>&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;  Integrated longitudinal programme: it could\r\nbe a good model in developing staff in surgical discipline.  Surgeons can accommodate themselves in this\r\nmodule without hampering their clinical practice , teaching, administrative responsibilities\r\nand research.<o></o></p><p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle">Drawback of this system is the time\r\nallocation. 10 to 20% time may not be sufficient to attain the skill.<o></o></p><p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><o> </o></p><p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" xss=removed>&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;c)<span xss=removed>      \r\n</span>&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;Peer coaching : I think it is not very effective\r\nin our socio cultural back ground, though it is very effective in open minded\r\neducated society. Taboo of feeling inferior getting some better learning form\r\njunior is not welcome  in our setting. We\r\nare to ignore our prejudices  .<o></o></p><p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" xss=removed>&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;d)<span xss=removed>     \r\n</span>&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;Computer aided learning/ E learning : tihis is\r\nvery effective in present time.  Certi\r\nficate  course in medical is an example\r\nwhere a medical facilitator can develop himself. Specially stucked in traffic\r\njam in Dhaka city this could be an ideal model \r\n.<o></o></p><p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle">Disadvantage of this system is cost and\r\navailability of gadgets.<o></o></p><p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle" xss=removed>&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;e)<span xss=removed>     \r\n</span>&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;Adoption of Linda Hutchison techniques:    safe environment, belonging  ,self-esteem, \r\nactualization build up capacity development  among learners were emphasized . medical\r\nsfaffs are exposed in different components of this technique to lear and\r\npractice these examples to up hold the teaching in surgical setting.  For example when new students are placed in\r\nthe surgery ward , many of them remain scared in handling the ugly  morphology/patholo gy of patients. If\r\nfacilitators can evoke self –esteem or belonging  or safe environment then intended  goals of surgical teaching  will be achieved.<o></o></p><p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><o> </o></p><p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><o> </o></p><p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"> <b>PHYSICAL \r\nENVIRONMENT :<o></o></b></p><p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><b> </b></p><p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle">it has a \r\ngreat effect among learners as well as facilitators. Right size\r\n&shape of class room, or ward space for teaching In clinical setting is\r\nimportant factor. We can easily understand the congested class room or ward\r\nspaces with distractive elements , as noise, crowd, unwanted movements\r\ncertainly hampers teaching and learning environment.<o></o></p><p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle">In clinical examination consent &\r\nprivacy maintainance   is utmost\r\nprerequisite. Teachers must be aware of it and administrator must give emphasis\r\non it in improving teaching environment .<o></o></p><p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><o> </o></p><p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"> <b>LOGISTIC SUPPORT:</b> allocation of\r\nadequate budget, supplying E learning equipments ,  printing hand outs , online free access,\r\nproviding  technical manpower are the\r\nimportant factors in developing staff & learning environment<o></o></p><p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><o> </o></p><p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpMiddle"><b>CONCLUSION:\r\n</b> To develop teachers capability, or\r\nto improve aptitude in teaching  needs\r\nmotivation, passion for teaching, and dedication. Professional development\r\nneeds multidisciplinary involvement. Any programme  should be customized  according to the need and requirement of\r\nfocused learners . this is very crucial in medical professional development. <o></o></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p class="MsoListParagraphCxSpLast"> <o></o></p>', NULL, '2018-02-10 04:37:28', 'F'),
(106, 56, 'Educational Environment & Staff Development', 'How to Improve Educational Environment & Plan to Staff Development In My Department', '2018-02-09 22:15:48', 'upload/attachment/6e4ef79e74d0b2b1fd4c246b935137d0.docx', '<p xss=removed><b><span xss=removed>How you\r\ncan improve the <u>educational environment of your own department</u>? <o></o></span></b></p><p xss=removed><b><span xss=removed>Following\r\nstrategies will be helpful to improve educational environment.<o></o></span></b></p><p xss=removed>&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;<span xss=removed>1.<span xss=removed>      \r\n</span></span>&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;<span class="mw-headline"><b><span xss=removed>Operational\r\ncharacteristics</span></b></span><span class="mw-headline"><span xss=removed>:</span></span><span xss=removed>The operation of the\r\neducational facility can have a determining role of the nature of the learning\r\nenvironment. Following operational  characteristics\r\nI  will adopt to improve the educational\r\nenvironment of my department:<o></o></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" xss=removed>&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;<span xss=removed>Ø<span xss=removed>  </span></span>&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;<span xss=removed>Preparing\r\n<b>academic calendar</b>  that must\r\ninclude detail</span><span xss=removed>class\r\nand activity schedules with duration, assessment, block schedule and vacation\r\netc.<o></o></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" xss=removed>&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;<span xss=removed>Ø<span xss=removed>  </span></span>&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;<span xss=removed>Academic calendar also\r\naccommodate some <b>space for reviewing own\r\nlearning</b> and space for learning of defaulter. <o></o></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" xss=removed>&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;<span xss=removed>Ø<span xss=removed>  </span></span>&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;<b><span xss=removed>Provision of mentoring</span></b><span xss=removed>:Mentoring\r\nwill alleviate the anxiety among the learners and help to overcome their\r\ndifficulties.Also will be helpful to find out the difficulties and\r\ninconsistences of leaning environment and thus remedial measure can be taken\r\naccordingly. </span><span xss=removed><o></o></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" xss=removed>&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;<span xss=removed>Ø<span xss=removed>  </span></span>&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;<b><span xss=removed>Learning\r\nstyle strategies</span></b><span xss=removed>:Encourage\r\nactive learning style and less dependency on direct instruction. Assignment\r\nworks, project work, guided or independent research, small group discussion,\r\ncollaborative and co-operative project encouraged.<o></o></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" xss=removed>&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;<span xss=removed>Ø<span xss=removed>  </span></span>&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;<b><span xss=removed>Flexible learning facilities</span></b><span xss=removed> with\r\nsafe and secured learning environment. </span><span xss=removed><o></o></span></p><p class="MsoNormal" xss=removed>&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;<strong><span xss=removed>Ø<span xss=removed> \r\n</span></span></strong>&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;<b><span xss=removed>Assessment\r\nstrategies:</span></b><span xss=removed> assessment\r\nis persistent, authentic,transparent, and never punitive.</span><strong><span xss=removed><o></o></span></strong></p><p class="MsoNormal" xss=removed>&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;<strong><span xss=removed>Ø<span xss=removed> \r\n</span></span></strong>&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;<strong><span xss=removed>There are constant opportunity for practice.</span></strong><strong><span xss=removed><o></o></span></strong></p><p class="MsoNormal" xss=removed>&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;<span xss=removed>Ø<span xss=removed>  </span></span>&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;<strong><span xss=removed>Curiosity\r\n: Questions are valued over answer</span></strong><b><span xss=removed><o></o></span></b></p><p class="MsoNormal" xss=removed><span xss=removed><o> </o></span></p><p xss=removed>&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;<span xss=removed>2.<span xss=removed>      \r\n</span></span>&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;<span class="mw-headline"><b><span xss=removed>Context of societal culture</span></b></span><span class="mw-headline"><span xss=removed>:</span></span><span xss=removed>Culture is generally defined as the beliefs, customs, arts,\r\ntraditions and values of anInstitution,society, group, place, or time. Culture\r\naffects the behavior of educators, students, staff, and community. It often determines\r\ncurriculum content. The socioeconomic status directly influences its ability to\r\nsupport a learning of an institution.<o></o></span></p><p xss=removed>&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;<span xss=removed>Ø<span xss=removed>  </span></span>&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;<span xss=removed>Select\r\nthe <b>vision and mission of the\r\ninstitution to provide quality education.</b><o></o></span></p><p xss=removed>&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;<span xss=removed>Ø<span xss=removed>  </span></span>&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;<b><span xss=removed>Committed to ensure</span></b><span xss=removed>\r\nthe effective learning environment by providing adequate resource, proper\r\nphysical facilities, and appropriate learning materials.<o></o></span></p><p xss=removed>&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;<span xss=removed>Ø<span xss=removed>  </span></span>&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;<span xss=removed>Allow\r\n<b>e-learning and encourage uses of other\r\neducational technologies</b> to maximus learning.<o></o></span></p><p xss=removed>&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;<span xss=removed>Ø<span xss=removed>  </span></span>&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;<b><span xss=removed>Recruit qualified faculties</span></b><span xss=removed>;\r\nMaintaining and ensuring provisions for continuous staff development\r\nstrategies.<o></o></span></p><p xss=removed>&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;<span xss=removed>Ø<span xss=removed>  </span></span>&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;<b><span xss=removed>Student support strategies</span></b><span xss=removed>\r\nshould be established and activate. Tutor schemes, peer support system, student\r\nadvisory office, email & internet.<o></o></span></p><p xss=removed>&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;<span xss=removed>3.<span xss=removed>      \r\n</span></span>&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;<span xss=removed>Physical setting: Classroom environment should have noise free,\r\ncomfortable, adequate space; appropriate workable teaching media and materials\r\nand other facilities need available.<o></o></span></p><p xss=removed>&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;<b><span xss=removed>a.<span xss=removed>       </span></span></b>&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;<span xss=removed>Ensure\r\nthe effective learning environment by providing <b>proper physical facilities, and appropriate learning materials<o></o></b></span></p><p xss=removed>&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;<span xss=removed>b.<span xss=removed>      \r\n</span></span>&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;<b><span xss=removed>Setting\r\nVLE (virtual learning environment</span></b><span xss=removed>) and distance learning\r\nprogram.<o></o></span></p><p xss=removed><b><span xss=removed>Following\r\nstrategies I will adopt for staff development of my department.<o></o></span></b></p><p xss=removed>&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;<span xss=removed>1.<span xss=removed>      \r\n</span></span>&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;<b><span xss=removed>Personal\r\nportfolio profile</span></b><span xss=removed>: encourage to submit the <b>strategies\r\nfor continuing Medical education & CPD program</b> for own development.\r\nMotivate the staff to be committed.<o></o></span></p><p xss=removed>&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;<span xss=removed>2.<span xss=removed>      \r\n</span></span>&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;<b><span xss=removed>Departmental\r\nstrategies</span></b><span xss=removed>: Aim is to promote <b>teaching\r\nas a scholarly activity and creating educational climate</b> that encourages\r\n& rewards educational leadership, innovation & excellence.<o></o></span></p><p xss=removed>&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;<span xss=removed>a.<span xss=removed>      \r\n</span></span>&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;<span xss=removed>Select the key content area- Whether Teaching-learning or\r\nResearch or Administration. Then select the sub-skill of each component.\r\nSuppose aim is to improve teacher’s skill in clinical teaching or lecturing, or\r\nsmall group discussion, or feedback, or evaluation.<o></o></span></p><p xss=removed>&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;<span xss=removed>b.<span xss=removed>      \r\n</span></span>&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;<span xss=removed>S<b>elect the strategies for\r\npersonal development, educational leadership, organizational development and\r\nchanges.</b> Also strategies in teaching specific content area like\r\ninter-professionalism, communication skill, or curriculum design.<o></o></span></p><p xss=removed>&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;<span xss=removed>c.<span xss=removed>       \r\n</span></span>&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;<span xss=removed>Determine the target  population:  All health care professional involve in\r\nteaching, organizational staff support teaching and organization etc.<o></o></span></p><p xss=removed>&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;<span xss=removed>3.<span xss=removed>      \r\n</span></span>&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;<b><span xss=removed>Select\r\nthe educational format,Implement & evaluate</span></b><span xss=removed>:\r\n<o></o></span></p><p xss=removed>&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;<span xss=removed>a.<span xss=removed>      \r\n</span></span>&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;<span xss=removed>Workshop, seminars, fellowship etc.<o></o></span></p><p xss=removed>&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;<span xss=removed>b.<span xss=removed>      \r\n</span></span>&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;<span xss=removed>Integrated longitudinal program can be adopted alternative to\r\nfellowship program where the faculty commit to use 10-20% of their time for\r\nnext 1-2yrs for maintaing teaching, research & administrative\r\nresponsibilities in addition to own development.<o></o></span></p><p xss=removed>&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;<span xss=removed>c.<span xss=removed>       \r\n</span></span>&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;<span xss=removed>Decentralized activates<o></o></span></p><p xss=removed>&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;<span xss=removed>d.<span xss=removed>      \r\n</span></span>&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;<span xss=removed>Peer-coaching<o></o></span></p><p xss=removed>&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;<span xss=removed>e.<span xss=removed>      \r\n</span></span>&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;<span xss=removed>Micro-teaching<o></o></span></p><p xss=removed>&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;<span xss=removed>f.<span xss=removed>        \r\n</span></span>&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;<span xss=removed>E-learning<o></o></span></p><p xss=removed>&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;<span xss=removed>4.<span xss=removed>      \r\n</span></span>&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;<b><span xss=removed>Mentorship</span></b><span xss=removed>:\r\ncommon strategies to promote socialization & development. Also balance  in three key element-support, challenge and\r\nvision for future<o></o></span></p><p xss=removed>&lt;!--[if !supportLists]--&gt;<span xss=removed>5.<span xss=removed>      \r\n</span></span>&lt;!--[endif]--&gt;<span xss=removed>Self directed learning program<o></o></span></p><p>\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n</p><p xss=removed><span xss=removed><o> </o></span></p>', NULL, '2018-02-10 04:15:48', 'F'),
(107, 70, 'Module Title: Contemporary Issues in Medical Education                 Subject: Staff Development and Educational Environment   Assignment:  Educational environment and staff development program of own department.', 'educational development and staff development', '2018-02-06 05:27:14', 'upload/attachment/1fb37934b484579aa1d53d859c526751.docx', '<p>Thanks for preparing assignment.  I have some observation as bellow:</p><p>In staff development program:</p><p xss=removed> your department/ institute should have have an strategies such as assessment of need, selection of key content are, Arrangement of appropriate method.</p><p xss=removed>The faculty also have some strategies and plan.</p><p>In educational environment:</p><p>Strategies for physical setting (classroom climate), Institutional culture,vision & mission, and  and educational approach should be mentioned</p><p>Pl rewrite and submit today.</p><p>thanks </p><p>Prof Md Shah Alam</p>', NULL, '2018-02-06 11:27:14', 'F');
