(108, 69, 'Write a plan to improve educational environment & how to improve staff development program of your own department.', '\r\n\r\nDr. Md. Towhidur Rahman         ID- GD2GOB\r\nName of the assignment – Write a plan to improve educational environment & how to improve staff development program of your own department.\r\nPlan to improve educational environment in my department (Radiology & Imaging) :\r\nLearning environment is an educational approach, cultural context, or physical setting in which teaching & learning occur. An improved learning environment is very important for achieving a successful educational outcome. We take a policy to develop our own strategy so that every faculty member can get a scope to develop their own carrier.\r\nStrategies to improve educational environment in my department -\r\n1. Physical settings – To build safe & supporting classroom by physically safe to students, noise free, comfortable, adequate seatings . Increase resources of libraries.\r\n2. To build & follow the academic calendar – strictly follow but if someone failed to attend there will be scope for rechance.\r\n3. Encouraging variety of active learning – project based learning, small group discussion, peer to peer learning, student-centered learning. Students must do more than just listen: students must read, write, discuss, or be engaged in solving problems.\r\n4. By encouraging e-learning.\r\n5. To create a learning culture into my department key steps are as - Formalize training and development plans by arrangement of workshops & seminars, give recognition to learning and to get feedback. \r\n6. Provision of mentoring may be added.\r\n7. Flexible learning may be applied in which attendance must.\r\n8. By encouraging question over answer for spirit of knowledge.\r\n9. To make policy for qualified faculty & staff development- By arrangement workshop, seminars, short courses, motivating  e-learning.\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\n\r\nHow to improve staff development program in my department (Radiology& Imaging)\r\nStaff development is a planned program designed to prepare institutions & faculty members for their various role. Staff development or faculty development has become an increasingly essential component in medical education. \r\nStrategies to improve staff development program in my department -\r\n1. Selection of target population –\r\nMedical teachers, course coordinator / curriculum planners, administrator, organizer, healthcare professional.\r\n2. Arrangement of appropriate methods –\r\na. Workshops- One of the most popular formats because of their inherent flexibility & promotion of active learning. Arrangement of workshops for improvement of teaching method & also for improving departmental environment.\r\nb. Seminars\r\nc. Short courses\r\nd. Motivating  e-learning.\r\n3. By adopting  the  following approaches faculty members can use a variety of methods according to assessment of need -\r\na. Microteaching\r\nb. Peer coaching\r\nc. Mentoring\r\nd. Feedback from learners\r\n4. The faculty also have some strategies and plan-\r\na. Teacher may be encouraged to determine their own needs through self reflection, evaluation by students & peer feedback.\r\nb. Encouraging students for asking questions.\r\nc. To build safe & supporting classroom.\r\n', '2018-02-06 17:26:52', 'upload/attachment/025891dc04a03b336ef1a57467c3294c.docx', '<p>Congratulation. your modified assignment is accepted. Please stay with CPD program.</p><p>Thanks</p><p>Prof Md Shah Alam</p>', NULL, '2018-02-06 23:26:52', 'F'),
